---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Word Hunt Solver"
  description="Learn how wordhuntsolver.ai collects, uses, and protects your data when you use our free word hunt solver tool."
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-700 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs italic text-brand-400 dark:text-brand-300">Written by admin</p>
    <p class="mt-4 rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 p-4 text-sm text-brand-600 dark:text-accent-300">
      Placeholder notice: replace the bracketed items below with your real analytics/ad setup before
      publishing, so this page matches your actual technical setup exactly.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      This Privacy Policy explains how wordhuntsolver.ai ("we", "our", "the site") collects and uses
      information when you use our word hunt solver and related tools. Effective date: [insert date].
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      We collect anonymous usage data through Google Analytics, such as pages visited, general location,
      and device type. If you contact us through the Contact form or email, we collect the name, email,
      and message you provide.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      We use this information to understand how the tool is used, fix bugs, and improve accuracy. We do
      not sell your personal information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Cookies and Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      This site uses Google Analytics, which sets cookies to measure traffic and usage. [Add a line here
      once you decide whether to also run ads, e.g. Google AdSense, and disclose it honestly.] You can
      disable cookies in your browser settings at any time, or opt out of Google Analytics using its
      official browser add-on.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      We do not share your personal data with third parties except as required by law or as needed to
      operate core site functions such as analytics.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      This site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information
      from children.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      Depending on your location, you may have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion
      of your personal data. Contact us using the details on our Contact page to make a request.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Changes To This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-brand-700 dark:text-white">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-brand-500 dark:text-brand-200">
      Questions about this policy? Reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="anchor-link">Contact Us</a> page.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
